,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T17:45:10.000Z","msg":"有人拍低左<br />\n<a href=\"https://video.twimg.com/ext_tw_video/1035173975377100801/pu/vid/1280x720/7cFQJ-1zsQZW1tHi.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo.twimg.com%2Fext_tw_video%2F1035173975377100801%2Fpu%2Fvid%2F1280x720%2F7cFQJ-1zsQZW1tHi.mp4&d=W3%2Boh2F6dMzMqcg9D7TjkZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=7c1a4639\" target=\"_blank\">https://video.twimg.com/ext_tw_video/1035173975377100801/pu/vid/1280x720/7cFQJ-1zsQZW1tHi.mp4</a>"},{"pid":"7841c73b47a8745532becf5b44dd636429dc7c08","tid":799783,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T17:46:30.000Z","msg":"IU&rsquo;s concerts usually last about 4 hours so she would always tell her young fans to go home earlier as she&rsquo;s worried about their safety at night. Last year IU told uaenas that she might hold a concert for teenage fans, &amp; now she&rsquo;s having a special 10th anniv fanmeet with them 😭"},{"pid":"a243d5814a770dd992403785820c80a92a52ab71","tid":799783,"uid":71497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T17:57:57.000Z","msg":"IU感謝祭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}